body: "Dependency path for minimatch: c8 -> test-exclude -> minimatch (9.x had ReDoS in pattern matching). Fixed by updating to c8 v11 which uses test-exclude v8 which depends on minimatch v10.\\n\\nDependency path for rollup: vitest -> @vitest/mocker -> vite -> rollup (4.57.1 had arbitrary file write via path traversal). Fixed by adding pnpm.overrides rollup >= 4.59.0.\\n\\nBoth are devDependencies and do not affect the published npm package or end users."
